{\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_landmark_stats\", \"description\": \"GET /api/landmarks/stats | 获取地标统计信息 | 获取地标统计信息（总数、按类别分布等）。不需 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {}, \"additionalProperties\": false}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_house_by_id\", \"description\": \"GET /api/houses/{house_id} | 根据房源 ID 获取详情 | 根据房源 ID 获取单套房源详情。无 query 参数，仅路径带 house_id，返回一条（安居客），便于智能体解析。调用时请求头必带 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"house_id\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=path | 房源 ID，如 HF_2001\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"house_id\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_house_listings\", \"description\": \"GET /api/houses/listings/{house_id} | 根据房源 ID 获取各平台挂牌记录 | 根据房源 ID 获取该房源在链家/安居客/58同城等各平台的全部挂牌记录。无 query 参数。调用时请求头必带 X-User-ID。响应 data 为 { total, page_size, items }。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"house_id\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=path | 房源 ID，如 HF_2001\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"house_id\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_houses_by_community\", \"description\": \"GET /api/houses/by_community | 按小区名查询可租房源 | 按小区名查询该小区下可租房源。默认每页 10 条、未传 listing_platform 时只返回安居客。用于指代消解、查某小区地铁信息或隐性属性。调用时请求头必带 X-User-ID。\", \"parameters\": {\"type\": \"object\", \"properties\": {\"community\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"description\": \"in=query | 小区名，与数据一致，如 建清园(南区)、保利锦上(二期)\"}, \"listing_platform\": {\"type\": \"string\", \"enum\": [\"链家\", \"安居客\", \"58同城\"], \"description\": \"in=query | 挂牌平台，不传则默认安居客\"}, \"page\": {\"type\": \"integer\", \"description\": \"in=query | 页码，默认 1\"}, \"page_size\": {\"type\": \"integer\", \"description\": \"in=query | 每页条数，默认 10，最大 10000\"}}, \"additionalProperties\": false, \"required\": [\"community\"]}}}, {\"type\": \"function\", \"function\": {\"name\": \"get_houses_by_platform\",